      },
      "lineNbr": 118,
      "author": {
        "id": 5649
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-06-25T14:56:57Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Good thought. I think we should now remove \"flags\" and just have the one signal (unchanged alpha) as the virtual. That would make it read a little easier, and remove this landmine.",
